            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200 font-medium">财富管理科技（WealthTech）</td>
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Robinhood, Betterment, Wealthfront, 富途牛牛</td>
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200 text-stone-600">降低投资门槛，用科技取代理财顾问，提供低费率自动化投资组合</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-stone-50">
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200 font-medium">保险科技（InsurTech）</td>
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Lemonade, Oscar Health, 众安保险</td>
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200 text-stone-600">用数据和算法精准定价，减少欺诈，提升理赔效率</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200 font-medium">基础设施（Infrastructure）</td>
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200">Plaid, MX, Marqeta, 银联</td>
            <td class="p-3 border border-stone-200 text-stone-600">为其他Fintech公司提供数据接口、账户连接、卡处理等基础服务</td>
          </tr>
